===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# A [[unit]] of the [[civil]] [[police]] who are specifically trained to serve duty on [[horseback#Adverb|horseback]]. Their duties can be [[ceremonial]], or often for crowd control, and to police areas of difficult access or [[wilderness]] areas.

====Usage notes====
* As a collective noun, the mounted police are referred to using plural pronouns and verb forms, such as ''they'' and ''were''.

